---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About me"
  description="Diogo Nunes, a Quality Advocate from Portugal who uses technology to improve people's lives."
  sideBarActiveItemID="about"
>
  <div class="mb-10 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold font-heading">About me 🦎</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
    <img
      src="/avatar.jpg"
      alt="Diogo Nunes"
      width="300"
      height="300"
      class="mask mask-circle mx-auto mb-8 block h-[10.2rem] w-[10.2rem] object-cover"
    />
    <div class="prose prose-lg mt-5 max-w-none text-center leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        My passion is using technology to improve people's lives. Professionally, I started as a developer, but now I'm
        a <strong>Quality Advocate (QA)</strong>: I help teams ship reliable software that delights their users.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work, I'm always building something. I'm an amateur
        <a href="/photos">photographer</a> whose photos have been viewed millions of times on Unsplash, and a
        <a href="/books">writer</a> of a couple of books. I was also a <a href="/blog/">blogger</a> for 9 years, a
        <a href="/pod">podcaster</a> for 2 years, and even a <a href="/projects/lenda-lenga">musician</a> once.
      </p>
      <p>
        Helping others fulfils me, so I volunteer a lot of my time: at conventions and local communities, writing
        <a href="https://github.com/dialex/">open source</a>,
        <a href="https://www.udemy.com/user/diogonunes4/">teaching</a> and <a href="/projects/pistae">mentoring</a>.
      </p>
      <p>I share what I learn so you can avoid my mistakes and build on my successes 😉</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center gap-4">
    <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/projects/">My projects</a>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://linkedin.com/in/nunesdiogo/" target="_blank">Let's connect!</a>
    <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/achievements/">My achievements</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
